 
<p>

Noam Chomsky: *Even without fundamental changes in prevailing state
capitalism, the kind of New Deal-style regulation that was dismantled
by the neoliberal assault can be <a href="https://www.commondreams.org/views/2022/07/28/noam-chomsky-we-can-free-ourselves-state-capitalism">reinstated, and strengthened</a>.*

 